word_mean_info__list.difference: 常指用胶水或浆糊粘贴，词义引申指坚持。
与stick的本义相同，指用胶水把东西粘合在一起，没有“坚持”的含义。
指物质微粒粘合在一起，成为不可分离的整体，强调所形成新物体的不可分割性。可引申指逻辑上的前后一致。
着重靠缠绕、紧抱、紧抓等方式而形成密切关系。也可作引申用。
正式用词，语气较严肃刻板，既可指物体粘在一起，也可指坚持信仰或忠于事业等。
多指走路爬山时用作支持或防卫使用的长木棒。
普通用词，指木制的细长手杖。
多指用藤或竹制成的细长的手杖。

list.abstract: stick（[stɪk]），英语单词，作名词时，为枯枝；枝条；像棍棒的东西。作动词时，为刺入；戳入；刺穿。短语搭配有stick with（继续使用）、stick to（继续做）。例句为“You will stick to your diet.（你要坚持节食。）”。 stick动词类近义词有extend、finger等，相关反义词有dislodge、move。现在分词为sticking，过去式为stuck。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm gonna stick with them.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想和他们在一起

yingyinNormal.en: Do you have any Chap Stick? Yeah.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们有护唇膏吗？有。

yingyinNormal.en: So stick to the program, soldier!
yingyinNormal.zh: 遵守程序士兵!

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, stick a fork in me, I am done.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你用叉子叉我，我熟了。

yingyinNormal.en: I really think we should stick with her.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我真觉得我们应该和她一起。

yingyinNormal.en: Would you like us to stick around for a while?
yingyinNormal.zh: 您介不介意我们先逗留一阵子？

yingyinNormal.en: Stick your right hand over the broom and say up.
yingyinNormal.zh: 右手放到扫帚的上方，然后说"起来"。

yingyinNormal.en: My name is Riley Matthews. Loves fish stick Fridays.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的名字是。莱丽·马修斯，喜欢吃每周五的鱼排。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, boy! Is that gonna stick? I'm already making t-shirts.
yingyinNormal.zh: 天啊！这个外号要永久使用了吗？我已经做好T恤了。

yingyinNormal.en: Can he handle the stick? Oh well... I can handle the stick.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他会开手动的车吗？ 哦…我会开手动的车！

yingyinNormal.en: You call that a glow stick? That is a glow stick. Come on, let's go.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你那玩意也敢叫荧光棒？这才是荧光棒。来吧，我们走。

yingyinNormal.en: It's a deal, Mr. Canning, but stick to it this time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 成交，坎宁先生，不过这次请信守承诺。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, I wanna quit, but then I think I should stick it out.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我想辞职，但我又觉得应该挺下去。

yingyinNormal.en: Now get your stick and get your ass on the stage. I can't.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拿好鼓槌滚上台去。我不行。

yingyinNormal.en: Gave him a ride. He took that photo of my hand on the stick.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我送了他一程。当我的手在控制杆上时，他拍这张照片。

yingyinNormal.en: So we've got a second wok here and this wok here is non-stick.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这里还有一口炒锅，是不粘锅。

yingyinNormal.en: We've all done very well. Why don't you just stick with stocks?
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们都做得很好，你为什么不专注于股票呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Get your stick and get your fucking ass on the stage. On stage.
yingyinNormal.zh: 拿好槌子滚上台。去上台。

yingyinNormal.en: Now usually my numbered stick would be read by a fortune teller.
yingyinNormal.zh: 通常是要把签条拿给算命先生看的。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't worry. I'll get the car keys out of the drain with a stick.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别担心，我可以用棍子把钥匙从下面弄出来。

examination_example.sentence: Amy then found a strong, straight <highlight>stick</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 艾米后来找到一根又直又结实的棍子。

examination_example.sentence: Paper, <highlight>sticks</highlight>, glue and string are all you need.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 纸张，木棍，胶水你所需要的就是这些。

examination_example.sentence: In the Song Dynasty, its producing area was changed into Huizhou, and it was then called the Hui Ink <highlight>Stick</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 在宋朝，它的产地迁到了徽州，于是后来人们称之为徽墨。

examination_example.sentence: We can learn from Mike that as long as we <highlight>stick</highlight> with what we like, we will be successful.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们可以从迈克那里学到，只要我们坚持自己喜欢的，我们就会成功。

examination_example.sentence: People who fear change often <highlight>stick</highlight> to a certain lifestyle.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 害怕改变的人往往坚持某种生活方式。

examination_example.sentence: "Well, if you <highlight>stick</highlight> to your dream, you will," the principal replied.
examination_example.sentence_trans: “嗯，如果你坚持你的梦想，你会的，”校长回答。

sense_info_list.en: be unable to get rid of or escape from

examination_example.sentence: He was <highlight>stuck</highlight>!
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他被卡住了！

examination_example.sentence: The things <highlight>stuck</highlight> between raised lines.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 东西卡在凸起的线条之间。

examination_example.sentence: her bike was too low to the ground and kept getting <highlight>stuck</highlight> on top of the bump．
examination_example.sentence_trans: 她的自行车离地太低，一直卡在颠簸的路面上。

sense_info_list.en: fasten with an adhesive material like glue

examination_example.sentence: Next they <highlight>stuck</highlight> the paper on the cross.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 接着，他们把纸粘贴在十字架（风筝骨架）上。

examination_example.sentence: We just <highlight>stick</highlight> it onto the fridge for a week or two and forget about it as soon as the paper disappears from there.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们只是把它贴在冰箱上一两个星期，等纸一不见了就忘了。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Sticking</highlight> chrysanthemum are also traditions to avoid the bad as (B) they have special smells which can repel (驱逐) insects and keep out the cold.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 贴菊花也是避凶的传统，因为菊花有特殊的气味，可以驱虫御寒。

examination_example.sentence: A true friend is one who <highlight>sticks</highlight> around in both the good times and the bad.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一个真正的朋友是无论顺境还是逆境都待在身边的人。

examination_example.sentence: A true friend will <highlight>stick</highlight> around when you are having a bad day.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当你过得不好的时候，一个真正的朋友会在你身边。

disambiguation_list.sense_disambiguation: 常指用胶水等黏性物质粘贴，词义引申指坚持。
与stick的本义相同，指用胶水把东西粘合在一起，没有"坚持"的含义。
